WEBVTT

00:04:29.123 --> 00:04:32.925
that requires knowing
how to act while waiting,

00:04:32.949 --> 00:04:36.668
the kind of patience I learned
with my grandmother's magic box.

00:04:37.865 --> 00:04:42.460
After all, we do not inherit
the earth from our ancestors.

00:04:43.030 --> 00:04:45.175
We borrow it from our children.

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:46.350
Thank you.

00:04:46.374 --> 00:04:51.230
(Applause)